-- Barclays names Kwan co-head of investment banking Asia-Pacific -memo
-- 
-- Sun Jul 13, 2014 09:32PM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, July 14 (Reuters) - Barclays Plc <BARC.L> has named Patrick Kwan and Reid Marsh as co-heads of investment banking in the Asia-Pacific region, according to an internal memo seen by Reuters on Monday.

Kwan, currently head of global finance and risk solutions for Asia-Pacific, joined Barclays in 2001. Reuters reported Marsh's appointment last week. He is London-based and will relocate to Hong Kong. [ID:nL6N0PJ4E3]